a:2:{s:7:"content";s:842:"<h1 class="text-center">How to add Information Zones</h1>
<p>It's really easy to add information zones using the Luminus RPG System. Just select the <code>info</code> object layer and add a rectangle where the player will be able to interact with the zone. Set a property to this rectangle called <code>message</code> of type <code>string</code>, then add yous message there. The Luminus Dialog Scene takes care of the rest. Oh! Talking about it, don't forget to launch it on your Scene.</p>
<p><a href="https://i.ibb.co/z5Ddzx5/Screen-Shot-2021-04-12-at-11-17-43.png" target="_blank"><img src="https://i.ibb.co/z5Ddzx5/Screen-Shot-2021-04-12-at-11-17-43.png" alt="" class="center" /></a></p>
